{"tid":2255630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(Liza姐與你穿越時空) 汪明荃與香港中樂團 2020","createTime":"2020-10-23T16:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T10:41:20.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0c28c8e2b368ca015140c69c51aac8f7555b32","tid":2255630,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"汪明荃與香港中樂團 2020<br />\n<br />\n地點：香港文化中心音樂廳<br />\n日期：11-12 Dec 2020 (Fri, Sat)<br />\n時間：8:00pm<br />\n票價：HKD 680 / 480 / 280  (*學生、長者、殘疾人士及綜援人士半價優惠)<br />\n<br />\nLiza姐與你穿越時空，古典詩詞、流行經典展風姿<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐」與樂團多次合作演出，擦出無限火花，今次與<br />\n你穿越時空，呈獻多首古典詩詞包括《花非花》、《聲<br />\n聲慢》、《紅豆詞》、《滿江紅》及首本名曲<span class=\"red\">《華麗轉<br />\n身》、《傾城之戀》、《歸帆》、《熱咖啡》</span>，展現綽<br />\n約風姿。<br />\n樂團特別委約著名香港作曲家伍卓賢創作以辛棄疾的宋<br />\n詞為題的《青玉案 &bull; 元夕》及以蘇軾的宋詞為題的《蝶<br />\n戀花 &bull; 春景》，於音樂會中作世界首演。<br />\n<br />\n指揮 Conductor：閻惠昌 Yan Huichang<br />\n演出者 Performed by：汪明荃 Liza Wang<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JuSZkko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJuSZkko.jpg&h=4ee50990&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34b4a886c8f254e81936af46b31e17a152659d58","tid":2255630,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1153291498081421/posts/3465357500208131/?vh=e&amp;extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1153291498081421%2Fposts%2F3465357500208131%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=445e7c4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1153291498081421/posts/3465357500208131/?vh=e&amp;extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;花非花&gt; 排練片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466141ee94c2186ec587d7db554a9d64bf581802","tid":2255630,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-1